        {
            "title": "百勝據悉正與LongRange就出售必勝客進行獨家談判",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據知情人士透露，百勝餐飲集團正在與LongRange Capital就出售必勝客連鎖業務進行獨家談判。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其中一位知情人士表示，LongRange近日與百勝進入獨家談判階段，擊敗了包括Sycamore Partners等其他競標者。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士透露，雙方正在就一項潛在協議進行深入磋商，該協議可能在幾周內達成。由於涉及未公開信息，知情人士要求匿名。他們補充說，目前尚無法保證最終能夠達成協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">百勝、LongRange和Sycamore的代表均拒絕置評。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-99b9c163-f6f0-3d0c-9e42-4abd6790a899-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">百勝去年表示已對必勝客展開戰略評估。該餐飲集團多年來一直在嘗試振興這個銷售持續停滯的連鎖品牌。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">私募股權公司LongRange成立於2019年。創始人Bob Berlin擁有餐飲行業經驗，在The Baupost Group任職期間曾主導對Arby’s的投資。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Yum Said to Be in Exclusive Talks to Sell Pizza Hut to LongRange</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%99%BE%E5%8B%9D%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E6%AD%A3%E8%88%87longrange%E5%B0%B1%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E5%BF%85%E5%8B%9D%E5%AE%A2%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4-215600350.html",
